description:
Sets the navigation layout type. Available types are:

- Frappe: Default left/right menu layouts
- Standard: Single navigation bar with dropdown menus merged in.
label: Layout Type
name: Website Theme-theme_navbar_type

description:
Overrides the default theme of the website on this page.

- Inherit: Will use base theme values where none are applied.
- Full: Will only use this theme's values ignoring base theme.
label: Theme Override Mode
name: Web Page-theme_override_mode
